sgruppas konklusjon, f\u00f8r hun konkluderer. Deretter kan dette bli en sak for styret ved St. Olav."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "78a4aeb3ef1d0a02ef357d6da34679d62972c5b2b42d64f2a480b35db0dbc4a6"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-01-22T13:48:08.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "\u2013 Dette rammer de sykeste av de syke, sier avdelingsleder P\u00e5l Sandvik."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article14091037.ece/mnhx0n/ALTERNATES/w980-default/psykiatri3.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/4caccc8435d9b84bfe92d9fb80dc04edaf9d10c2.jpg?5995dbc0"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Vil kutte tilbud ved \u00d8stmarka -adressa.no", "Isolert seg", "God plass", "Flytter penger", "F\u00e6rre ansatte"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "4caccc8435d9b84bfe92d9fb80dc04edaf9d10c2"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["St. Olavs Hospital", "psykiatri", "\u00d8stmarka"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "St. Olavs Hospital,psykiatri,\u00d8stmarka"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["psykisk helsevern", "pasient", "behandle", "tilbud", "kutte tilbud", "liv", "f\u00e6rre ansatte", "lukket avdeling", "distriktspsykiatriske senter"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["st. olav", "\u00f8stmarka", "olavs hospital", "st. olavs hospital", "nidaros"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["anne-marit stokke", "bj\u00f8rn seljeflot", "liv sj\u00f8vold", "morten schou", "p\u00e5l sandvik"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["pluss", 